data.description: Look no further than this spacious three bedroom, two bathroom home! This property is bursting with potential and is just waiting for the right buyer to make it their own. From the time you walk in, the open floor plan from the living room to the dining and kitchen creates an inviting atmosphere. Fresh new paint inside and out, and new carpet was installed throughout the home in Dec 2022. The kitchen offers plenty of cabinet space, a separate utility room with full size washer and dryer hook ups, and a large 2 car garage that includes an extra storage closet. The spacious bedrooms include ceiling fans, and offer ample closet space. With a little imagination and some TLC, the bathrooms could be transformed and updated to your perfect sweet escape. This property includes a large backyard and a large patio that would be great for BBQ's or entertaining! Seller offering $10,000 in concessions.
